{"tid":675924,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"[農藥都假]不滿新官上任男子在其水壺下毒","createTime":"2018-05-24T03:03:03.000Z","updateTime":"2018-05-24T03:20:44.000Z","uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"5b667abba2ff14659f6cfe818dcb61aa247a3acb","tid":675924,"uid":63909,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:03:03.000Z","msg":"陝西寧陝縣煙草專賣局的副局長熊博，因為不滿意新上任的趙副局長，在趙副局長的水壺中加入農藥「滅掃利」。<br />\n<br />\n趙副局長其後身體不適送院，熊博就被行政拘留10天和罰款500元，同時接受黨內嚴重警告和調職處分。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/05/24/110257_043ab0ec0976b0963523d742dc22973c.PNG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F05%2F24%2F110257_043ab0ec0976b0963523d742dc22973c.PNG&h=76084e05&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1724769147667564/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fcablechinadesk%2Fvideos%2F1724769147667564%2F&d=24PkLJ6Ty%2FO0VFS1NGPvh5ZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=2bcaa40e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/cablechinadesk/videos/1724769147667564/</a>"},{"pid":"26b1eb13c204d0ed5fef347913708babed4d1518","tid":675924,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:04:27.000Z","msg":"落毒都係行政拘留10天和罰款500元<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7c3f3058d5a7cd5884338d82fdcaa44cc5496a93","tid":675924,"uid":170229,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"26b1eb13c204d0ed5fef347913708babed4d1518","tid":675924,"uid":63909,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:04:27.000Z","msg":"落毒都係行政拘留10天和罰款500元<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-05-24T03:20:44.000Z","msg":"有後台，隨意啦<br />\n好似警察咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 做錯都會俾人保"}]}